.SS Combined content and network analysis with similarity filtering:
.EX
{
  "ignoreDomains": ["google.com", "googlee.com"],
  "ignore_similar": true,
  "ignore_similar_threshold": 75,
  "ignore_similar_ignored_domains": true,
